## Latest Mergers and Acquisitions
In June 2024, Chime Financial Inc., a US-based financial services company, acquired Salt Labs Inc. for an undisclosed amount.

## Market Definition
The personal finance apps market includes revenues earned by entities by providing bank accounting integration, credit score monitoring, and investment tracking.

